    <!-- Why Goose Creek -->
    <section class="section light">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Why Goose Creek Is a Prime Market for Direct Mail</h2>
                <p>Goose Creek is one of the fastest-growing suburban communities in the Lowcountry, with a strong military presence, young families, and affordable housing driving steady population growth.</p>
